==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bur fish
<hw>Bur" fish`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A spinose,
plectognath fish of the Atlantic coast of the United States (esp.
<spn>Chilo mycterus geometricus</spn>) having the power of distending
its body with water or air, so as to resemble a chestnut bur; -- called
also <altname>ball fish</altname>, <altname>balloon fish</altname>, and
<altname>swellfish</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Burg</ent>⟦br⟧
